      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I've tested dozens of project management tools over the years. Some are too simple. Others feel like they were designed by engineers who never actually managed a team. Then there's monday.com — a platform that somehow nails the sweet spot between powerful and intuitive.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If you've been searching for a tool that lets your entire team see what's happening, who's doing what, and where things stand at a glance, keep reading. This might be the last \"which project tool do we use?\" conversation your team ever has.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l0",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://try.monday.com/i32p0zf6vr81"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
