            "marks": [
              "l0"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What Is monday.com?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "monday.com is a visual work management platform built on what the company calls a \"Work OS.\" That's a fancy way of saying it's a flexible system where you can plan, track, and manage virtually any type of work — all through colorful, drag-and-drop boards.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Think of it this way: instead of drowning in spreadsheets, email threads, and Slack messages, your team gets a single hub where everything lives. Projects, client work, internal processes, sprint planning, content calendars — monday.com handles it all through customizable boards, columns, and views.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Here's what makes it different from the tools you might have tried before: monday.com doesn't force you into a rigid structure. You build your workspace around how your team actually works. Marketing teams use it one way. Software teams use it another. Construction companies, agencies, nonprofits — they all mold it to fit their reality.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The platform launched in 2012 and has grown to serve over 180,000 customers worldwide, including companies like Coca-Cola, Universal Studios, and HubSpot. But it's not just for enterprises. The free plan and affordable tiers make it accessible for freelancers, startups, and small teams too.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l1",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/how-to-use-monday-com"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Want a deeper walkthrough? Check out our ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "step-by-step guide on how to use monday.com",
            "marks": [
              "l1"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ".",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Core Features That Make monday.com Shine",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Let me walk you through the features that actually matter in day-to-day work — not the marketing fluff, but the stuff you'll use constantly.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Visual Boards",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This is the heart of monday.com. Every project, process, or workflow lives on a board. Each board contains items (rows) and columns that hold different types of data — status, dates, people, numbers, files, you name it. The default view is a colorful table, but you can switch to Kanban, Gantt timeline, calendar, map, chart, or workload views with a single click.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The visual nature means you can spot bottlenecks instantly. A column full of red \"stuck\" statuses? That's your signal to jump in. No digging required.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "200+ Templates",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Starting from scratch can feel overwhelming. monday.com ships with over 200 pre-built templates for everything from product roadmaps to event planning to CRM tracking. Pick one, tweak it in five minutes, and you're rolling.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Docs",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "monday.com Docs lets your team create and collaborate on documents right inside the platform. The real magic? You can pull live data from your boards directly into docs. So your project brief can auto-update with the latest deadlines and statuses. No more stale documents floating around.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Automations",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This is where monday.com saves you serious time. Set up if-then rules without writing a single line of code. Examples:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "When a status changes to \"Done,\" notify the client automatically.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "When a deadline arrives, move the item to the \"Overdue\" group.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "When a new item is created, assign it to a specific person.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l2",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/monday-com-tips"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "You can automate repetitive tasks in minutes, and the system just runs in the background. For more tips on building efficient workflows, see our ",
            "marks": []
