      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Dashboards",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Need the big picture? Dashboards pull data from multiple boards into visual widgets — charts, numbers, progress bars, battery indicators. Perfect for managers who want a real-time snapshot without pinging five people for updates.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Mobile Apps",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "iOS and Android apps keep you connected on the go. Review boards, update statuses, reply to comments — all from your phone. The mobile experience is genuinely good, not a watered-down afterthought.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What's New and Exciting",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "monday.com keeps shipping updates at a pace that's hard to match. Here's what's generating buzz right now:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "AI Features",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The platform has integrated AI capabilities starting from the Basic plan. You get 1,000 AI credits per month (with the option to add more anytime). What can AI do inside monday.com? Summarize long threads, generate task descriptions, build formulas, and help you write content — all without leaving the platform. It's the kind of AI integration that actually saves time instead of feeling like a gimmick.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
