      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "For power users, formula columns let you run calculations across your data. Mirror columns pull information from connected boards, creating relationships between projects. It's spreadsheet-level power with a fraction of the complexity.",
