        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "monday.com's biggest differentiator is its visual-first approach combined with extreme flexibility. Unlike rigid tools, you build boards around your actual workflow. The color-coded status system, 200+ templates, no-code automations, and AI features starting from the Basic plan create a platform that's both powerful and immediately intuitive.",
