            "_type": "span",
            "text": "For small to mid-sized sales teams, absolutely. monday.com includes CRM templates with pipeline tracking, lead management, deal stages, and contact organization. You can automate follow-ups, track revenue, and view dashboards — all without paying for a separate CRM tool. Larger enterprises may still prefer dedicated CRM platforms, but many teams find monday.com covers their needs perfectly.",
